author: veithen
msg: Schedule unused base64 codec code for removal. Other libraries do a better job than this code (see e.g. AXIOM-434) and we don't want to fix/maintain it if we don't use it ourselves.

author: veithen
msg: Deprecate the capability to store a char[] (instead of a String) in an OMText. There is no known usage of that feature, there is no documentation and it is ill defined (e.g. is it legal to modify the array returned by getTextCharacters?).

author: tilman
msg: PDFBOX-2783: Use getCOSObject() instead of getCOSDictionary()
